siconos (4.0.0-1ubuntu9) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Make siconos-mechanics-tools a Python package, depend on python-siconos.
  * Fix error in removing Thumbs.db files.
  * Update README.Debian.
  * Fix siconos-doc section.
  * Fix some bad old script hashbangs.
    This should be fixed upstream.
  * Fix jquery.js references in doxygen html.
  * Add gbp.conf
  * Ignore quilt dir
  * Patch remove renderer sources.
  * Fix empty-binary-package
  * Use dh_installexamples and put examples fixes under install not fixperms.
  * Remove Thumbs.db.gz files.
  * Fix architecture and section of docs and examples
  * Fix configuration of LDFLAGS
  * Remove use of rpath (binary-or-shlib-defines-rpath)
  * Set the soname properly, and set it to 0.
  * Remove bad parallel option.
  * Use brackets on component variable during include install loop.
  * Remove pprocess, it's broken in this release and requires OCC.
  * Add man pages for 'siconos' and 'vview' using help2man.
  * Remove erroneous bit in the man pages about info and add website instead.

