siconos (4.0.0-1ubuntu8) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Set standards version to 3.9.7 for Xenial.
  * Fix libbulletcollision version (package name) dependency for Xenial.
  * Rename siconos-mechanics, siconos-mechanics-io to siconos-mechanics-tools.
  * Fix -dev dependencies and remove python:Depends where not needed.
  * Fix lintian error non-dev-pkg-with-shlib-symlink
  * Fix dependency siconos -> siconos-mechanics-tools
  * Fix dependency libsiconos-numerics -> lp-solve
  * Fix section for -dev packages.
  * Set debian/copyright info.
  * Fix lintian extended-description-line-too-long
  * Add linker flag '-Wl,--as-needed' to remove unneeded library deps.
  * Remove ${shlibs:Depends} for packages that don't include a shared library.
  * Better fix for stp file perms, and also fix more files in examples.

